Coursera's Algorithms Design and Analysis I: slides and F# source code

The slides and assignments for Algorithms Design and Analysis I on Coursera.

Each assignment consists of the main algorithm, test scripts and test cases written in FSUnit and xUnit. A few input files are dropped because their sizes are too big.
